headline: Corporate CFOs Think a Recession Is Coming. Here Are 3 Stocks to Own If They're Right.
summary: The latest CNBC CFO Council Survey found that 60% of CFOs expect a U.S. recession later in 2025.  Another 15% predict a recession next year.  Ninety percent of the CFOs surveyed believe President Trump's tariffs will cause inflation to rise.
